IMPORTANT GENERAL INFORMATION
AIR FREIGHT
Personalized "Hot Pack" Service Airport to Airport.
Freight $11.00 minimum per shipment. Rate 14 cents lb., plus 5 percent
Federal Tax.
BAGGAGE
Free allowance is 40 pounds, including briefcase and hand luggage.
Excess baggage may be accepted, space and weight permitting, and will be
charged at the rate of 14 cents per pound, $2.00 minimum.
CHECK-IN TIME FOR FLIGHTS
In the interest of on-time service to all passengers, please be at the airport
counter 20 minutes prior to scheduled flight time. Reservations not claimed
20 minutes prior to scheduled flight are subject to cancellantion.
PAYMENTS
In addition to cash, SK YSTREAM accepts Master Charge, Bank Americard,
Carte Blanche,
Diners Club, Interbank, American Express Credit Cards.
WEATHER DELAYS OR CANCELLATIONS
SKYSTREAM AIRLINES will not be responsible for passenger's travel or
overnight expenses when flights are delayed or cancelled due to weather.
The passenger will receive space on the first available flight, or the unused
portion of the ticket will be refunded.
